Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}My name is Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,五年裡  我被困在地獄一般的小島上\N{\b0\fs12}After five years on a hellish island,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來只有一個目標\N{\b0\fs12}I have come home with only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我的城市\N{\b0\fs12}to save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但要達到目標  我不能像過去一樣成為兇手\N{\b0\fs12}But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,為了紀念我的朋友  我只能偽裝成另一個人\N{\b0\fs12}To honor my friend's memory, I must be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}深切懷念托馬斯•梅林\N孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,成為另一種存在\N{\b0\fs12}I must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你能說你沒有濫用藥物嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You're telling me you don't have a substance abuse problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,地檢辦給了一筆很可觀的解雇補償金\N{\b0\fs12}The D.A.'s office has a generous severance package.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我去跟檢察官親自解釋一下好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Wait, let me explain to the D.A.--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  但是你被解雇了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry, but you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候做出選擇了  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Time to choose, Oliver,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,選出誰生  誰死\N{\b0\fs12}who lives and who dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到了你想要的東西\N{\b0\fs12}You got what you came for!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-時間到  -你這變態的神經病\N{\b0\fs12}- Time's up. - You freaking psychopath!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\b0\fs12}No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊被注射了血清\N{\b0\fs12}Roy was injected with the serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得看著他\N{\b0\fs12}We are going to have to keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  停下  他快死了\N{\b0\fs12}Roy! Stop it, you're killing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你更快更強了\N{\b0\fs12}You're stronger, you heal faster,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你卻控制不了自己\N{\b0\fs12}but you're not in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以教你  讓我幫你吧\N{\b0\fs12}I can teach you. Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們什麼時候開始\N{\b0\fs12}When do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,給你帶來個新客人\N{\b0\fs12}Got your latest customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這位天才竟然去搶\N{\b0\fs12}Genius who held up the convenience store
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,警局對面的便利店\N{\b0\fs12}across the street from a police precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這計劃可不明智\N{\b0\fs12}Not the smartest plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,走過來\N{\b0\fs12}Come on through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,膝蓋有傷\N{\b0\fs12}Bum knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,幾年前動過手術\N{\b0\fs12}I had it replaced a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那還是用老辦法吧\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I guess we'll have to do this old-fashioned-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起胳膊\N{\b0\fs12}Arms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,給你找了個新獄友\N{\b0\fs12}Got your new bunk mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,別惹事\N{\b0\fs12}Play nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你是本•特納嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Ben Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚\N{\b0\fs12}Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜  紅林路和燕草大道\N{\b0\fs12}Midnight. Redwood Drive and Larkspur Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,紅林路和燕草大道  屋頂  去那裡\N{\b0\fs12}Redwood and Larkspur. The rooftop. Be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒四下看看嗎\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know if you've looked around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒法自由出入這地方\N{\b0\fs12}but we don't exactly have in and out privileges here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我兒子跟他媽在一起\N{\b0\fs12}My son is with his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我是再也見不到他了\N{\b0\fs12}I won't get to see him, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣做  他就沒事\N{\b0\fs12}This way, he's set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我完成這事  他就能拿到錢\N{\b0\fs12}I do this, he gets the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,完成什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,該死\N{\b0\fs12}Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼也沒做\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再來\N{\b0\fs12}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天是在拍水\N{\b0\fs12}You know, I slapped water out of a bowl yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,前天也是在拍水\N{\b0\fs12}And I slapped water out of a bowl the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定很擅長了\N{\b0\fs12}You must be getting pretty good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我已經等不及被狗糧攻擊了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, well, I can't wait to get attacked by a dog dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是射手鍛煉臂力的方法\N{\b0\fs12}This is how an archer builds arm strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你難道不知道嗎\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not sure if you've been paying attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,力量對我來說不是問題\N{\b0\fs12}but strength isn't my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對  但控制力量是你的問題\N{\b0\fs12}No, controlling it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再來\N{\b0\fs12}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就因為這樣\N{\b0\fs12}And that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你上周才把一個人打到進醫院\N{\b0\fs12}is how you put a guy in the hospital last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道的\N{\b0\fs12}How'd you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這事跟你沒關係\N{\b0\fs12}It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你答應讓我幫你的時候\N{\b0\fs12}You made it my business
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這事就跟我有關係了\N{\b0\fs12}when you agreed to let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前認識一個像你這樣的人\N{\b0\fs12}I knew someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,注射了米拉庫魯的人\N{\b0\fs12}Someone injected with the Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}He was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這血清扭曲了他的心智\N{\b0\fs12}But it warped his mind to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以至於我都認不出他了\N{\b0\fs12}where I didn't even recognize him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這人是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who was this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼從沒聽說過他\N{\b0\fs12}How come I've never heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒聽說過米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}Or that Mirakuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還有什麼他的事你能告訴我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is there anything you can tell me about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我用一支箭射穿了他的眼\N{\b0\fs12}I had to put an arrow through his eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我沒看錯的話  斯萊德在洞裡\N{\b0\fs12}If I'm reading this right, then Slade is back at the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他為什麼要去墓地那裡\N{\b0\fs12}Well, why would he go back to where the graves are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他就知道了\N{\b0\fs12}We'll find out when we find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他的時候  你不能跟他說\N{\b0\fs12}And when we do... you can't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Tell him what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別對我像個外人似的\N{\b0\fs12}Don't talk to me like I'm other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你臉上就是這種表情\N{\b0\fs12}You've got that look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們第一次接吻時就是這種表情\N{\b0\fs12}The same one that you had after the first time we kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,純粹內疚的表情\N{\b0\fs12}Pure guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我就是很內疚  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Because I am guilty, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我  艾沃才殺了莎朵\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo killed Shado because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的\N{\b0\fs12}But that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是這樣\N{\b0\fs12}And even if it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你告訴斯萊德是因為你\N{\b0\fs12}nothing good comes from telling Slade
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,害死了他愛的女人\N{\b0\fs12}that you think you're responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,對你沒有任何好處\N{\b0\fs12}for the death of the woman he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,愛是最強大的情感\N{\b0\fs12}Love's the most powerful emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它也是最危險的\N{\b0\fs12}And that makes it the most dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,說得真好\N{\b0\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道怎麼去洞穴嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You still know how to get to the cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這條路\N{\b0\fs12}It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼在家\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為你留在羅伊家了\N{\b0\fs12}I thought you were staying at Roy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想自己待一會\N{\b0\fs12}Just needed a little "me" Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼穿得這麼隆重\N{\b0\fs12}What's with the fancy fancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我要出去吃飯\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I'm-- I'm going out to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跟沃爾特一起\N{\b0\fs12}With Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,算是約會嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Like a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只是吃晚飯\N{\b0\fs12}Like a dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話  我也不知道今晚算什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Truly, I don't know what the evening holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我沒事\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是\N{\b0\fs12}Mostly. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊的事\N{\b0\fs12}It's Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他上周遇上點麻煩\N{\b0\fs12}He had some trouble last week, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而我不知道怎麼幫他\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know how to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓我留在家裡嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you want me to stay home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以給沃爾特打個電話  重新再約\N{\b0\fs12}I can call Walter and we can reschedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不用\N{\b0\fs12}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你和沃爾特準備重歸於好\N{\b0\fs12}If you and Walter are going to patch things up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不給你壓力  但你一定要去\N{\b0\fs12}No pressure. But you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可能沒什麼\N{\b0\fs12}It may be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一個辦法才能知道\N{\b0\fs12}Only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意  老爸  進來吧\N{\b0\fs12}No, please, dad, come right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你已經把房子住得很破爛了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I guess you're going for that lived-in look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有工作請不起管家\N{\b0\fs12}Can't afford a housekeeper without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,酒錢倒是挺足的\N{\b0\fs12}Got enough beverage money, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想吵架\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to need to crack
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先讓我再開一瓶酒吧\N{\b0\fs12}open another bottle if we're going to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來吵架的\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't come here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那你來幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我過得挺好的  真的\N{\b0\fs12}Because I'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,實際上  我有個工作面試\N{\b0\fs12}In fact, I have a job interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是喬安娜的新公司\N{\b0\fs12}At Joanna's new firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的  不錯\N{\b0\fs12}That's good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我來這裡的真正原因是\N{\b0\fs12}But the real reason I came here is--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是你覺得你需要每週定量的來\N{\b0\fs12}Is because you realized that you didn't reach your weekly quota
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,揭示我的生活如何不堪\N{\b0\fs12}of reminding me of how much I'm ruining my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為我想你了  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}It's 'cause I miss you, Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,長久以來  我們相依為命\N{\b0\fs12}For a long time, it was just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Whatever else was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不管對方有多糟糕\N{\b0\fs12}no matter how bad either of us was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們誰都不會不管對方\N{\b0\fs12}we didn't disappear on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的家人\N{\b0\fs12}Because you're my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而我想念我的家人\N{\b0\fs12}And I miss my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要不要一起吃個晚餐\N{\b0\fs12}So how about we have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我  今晚\N{\b0\fs12}You and me, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經吃過了\N{\b0\fs12}I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那明晚呢\N{\b0\fs12}How about tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\b0\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,明晚晚餐\N{\b0\fs12}Dinner tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和羅伊怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}How's it going with Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}Not well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟這孩子不熟\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know the kid all too well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他看起來充滿了憤怒\N{\b0\fs12}but he seems to be five kinds of angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你低估他了\N{\b0\fs12}You might be underestimating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊在注射米拉庫魯前就很憤青了\N{\b0\fs12}Roy was mad at the world before he was injected with Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你說你有過類似經歷\N{\b0\fs12}You say you've seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜  他曾是我朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson. He was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你故意使用了過去時\N{\b0\fs12}Troubling use of past tense there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我可以幫助他控制住\N{\b0\fs12}I thought I could help him control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我錯了\N{\b0\fs12}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是現在我知道的更多了  我不會在\N{\b0\fs12}But I know more now, and I'm not going
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊身上犯同樣的錯誤了\N{\b0\fs12}to make the same mistake with Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵山監獄  鑒於他們那可悲的安保能力\N{\b0\fs12}Iron Heights. Due to their low security post-quake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得應該花些時間監視一下\N{\b0\fs12}I thought it would be a good idea to keep an eye on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的內部通訊系統\N{\b0\fs12}their internal communication for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你黑進了監獄內部系統\N{\b0\fs12}You hacked into a prison system network?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在批判我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that judgment I'm hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,驕傲\N{\b0\fs12}Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵山監獄剛對本•特納下了通牒\N{\b0\fs12}Iron Heights just put out a bolo for Ben Turner,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是青銅虎  順便說一句\N{\b0\fs12}Aka Bronze Tiger, which, btw,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這真是個爛綽號  老虎不是青銅色的\N{\b0\fs12}is a terrible nickname, because tigers are not bronze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,特納逃跑了\N{\b0\fs12}Turner escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,出去時殺了十個守衛\N{\b0\fs12}Killed ten guards on his way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這事肯定會上新聞\N{\b0\fs12}You think that would have made the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵山監獄保密的能力\N{\b0\fs12}Iron Heights is better at keeping secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,比他們看管囚犯的能力強多了\N{\b0\fs12}than they are at keeping prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,知道他可能去哪嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Any idea where he's headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,找出來\N{\b0\fs12}Get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你們的人到別處去\N{\b0\fs12}Tell your men to take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,走開\N{\b0\fs12}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,武器可以放在這\N{\b0\fs12}They can leave their weapons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝您的提前釋放\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you for the early release.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,本來想就這麼走的  但是我\N{\b0\fs12}Thought about taking off, but I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很好奇\N{\b0\fs12}curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會幫個陌生人逃獄啊\N{\b0\fs12}Who would break a stranger out of prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想讓那罪犯幫忙的人\N{\b0\fs12}Someone who wishes to hire you for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要幫忙找回一樣東西\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to help my men retrieve a certain item.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個\N{\b0\fs12}This is the item.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你見過  對吧\N{\b0\fs12}You know it, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,確實\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道還缺什麼嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you know what you're missing with here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不菲的價格\N{\b0\fs12}Won't be cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,錢不是問題\N{\b0\fs12}This is not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道它有百人以上的殺傷力吧\N{\b0\fs12}You do know that thing could kill hundreds of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不對  特納先生\N{\b0\fs12}No, Mr. Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是千人以上\N{\b0\fs12}It will kill thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,該你了\N{\b0\fs12}Now you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢來\N{\b0\fs12}Go slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,停\N{\b0\fs12}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在教你出拳\N{\b0\fs12}This is not about learning to throw a punch,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是在教你力度控制\N{\b0\fs12}this is about learning to control your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,先是打水花  現在又是這個\N{\b0\fs12}First water slapping, now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候才能玩完這些\N{\b0\fs12}When are you going to run out of ways
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看起來很蠢的把戲\N{\b0\fs12}to make me look stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我能學到的就只有怎麼被惹毛\N{\b0\fs12}All I'm learning is new ways to get pissed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,順便說一句\N{\b0\fs12}and in case you haven't noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來就擅長被惹毛\N{\b0\fs12}I'm already pretty good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,憤怒並非無益  羅伊  力量就來自憤怒\N{\b0\fs12}There's nothing wrong with anger, Roy. Anger is energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得學習用好的方式使用它\N{\b0\fs12}but you need to learn to channel it in a positive way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,比如打擊那些破壞城市的人\N{\b0\fs12}Like putting the hurt on guys going after the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就不讓我打個能反擊的目標嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Let me try hitting something that'll actually hit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,時候未到\N{\b0\fs12}Too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,帶我去一次\N{\b0\fs12}Get me out there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就一晚上\N{\b0\fs12}One night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這些蠢東西也能好接受些\N{\b0\fs12}All this, it would be a lot easier to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為是二人晚餐呢\N{\b0\fs12}Ah. I didn't realize we'd have company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這位是馬克•法蘭西斯\N{\b0\fs12}This is Mark Frances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他是卡達克集團的首席財務官\N{\b0\fs12}Mark's CFO at Kardak Holdings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們曾在政黨選舉指導委員會共事過\N{\b0\fs12}We've been putting in some hours with the party's election steering committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你\N{\b0\fs12}It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最近高興見我的人可不多了\N{\b0\fs12}Those are words I'm not accustomed to hearing these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是像母獅一樣在保護自己的孩子們\N{\b0\fs12}You were a lioness doing what she had to do to protect her cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,星城很多人都像我一樣\N{\b0\fs12}You know, I'm not the only person in Starling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,站在你這邊\N{\b0\fs12}who sees it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的安慰\N{\b0\fs12}That's a comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,實話實說而已  請坐\N{\b0\fs12}It's the truth. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不常見你對政治\N{\b0\fs12}Well, it's unlike you to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如此興趣濃厚呢  沃爾特\N{\b0\fs12}show such an interest in politics, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我星城國家銀行新工作的一部分\N{\b0\fs12}It's part of my new position at the Starling National Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,董事會很關注\N{\b0\fs12}My board of directors is very concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,星城的發展方向\N{\b0\fs12}about the trajectory of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是說塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德  -是的\N{\b0\fs12}- You mean Sebastian Blood. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們相信他的政策會讓\N{\b0\fs12}We believe that his policies will bankrupt Starling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,星城在八個月之內破產\N{\b0\fs12}within the next eight months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但平常選民卻不關注此事\N{\b0\fs12}Not that the average voter cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都被他的魅力俘獲了\N{\b0\fs12}They're all caught up in his charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且沒有可以與他匹敵的對手\N{\b0\fs12}And he's not running against a viable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他打敗了我們所有重點培養的候選人\N{\b0\fs12}Blood's trounced every potential candidate we've focus-tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不過制度方面是他的弱項\N{\b0\fs12}But we believe that he's vulnerable on regulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是又能怎樣呢\N{\b0\fs12}Even if he is, it hardly matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,銀行政策只是證交會的問題\N{\b0\fs12}Banking regulations are an SEC issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,星城需要的是城市層面的對抗\N{\b0\fs12}Starling City needs to use the means at a city's disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特說過你很聰明\N{\b0\fs12}Walter said you were smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但你沒邀請我吃晚餐  聽我的意見\N{\b0\fs12}But you didn't invite me to dinner to hear my opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你想瞭解我的位置\N{\b0\fs12}You want to hear my positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓我去對抗塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德\N{\b0\fs12}You want me to run against Sebastian Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  我快餓死了  我們要去哪兒\N{\b0\fs12}Dad, I'm starving. Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這兒有個小店\N{\b0\fs12}It's little hole in the wall right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  等一下\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,別碰我\N{\b0\fs12}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信你會做這樣的事情\N{\b0\fs12}I can't believe you would do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,否則你也不會來呀\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you wouldn't have come otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你說對了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  你需要幫助\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, you need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那也用不著他們\N{\b0\fs12}Not from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那間屋子裡沒有一個人\N{\b0\fs12}There is not one person in that room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我所經歷的痛苦\N{\b0\fs12}who knows what I have been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的沒錯  他們之中有人承受過比你更痛苦的事情\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, you're right. Some of them, they've been through worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不管怎樣\N{\b0\fs12}But for better or worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,每一個人走進那間屋子都是因為需要\N{\b0\fs12}everyone in that room needs to be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你也需要去那\N{\b0\fs12}and you need to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為只有你失去過愛人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You think you're the only person that's ever lost someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你被炒過魷魚  只有你曾經把生活搞的一團糟嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Who ever got fired, who ever got their lives into a mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子  你好好想想  不是只有你最慘\N{\b0\fs12}You think again, kiddo, 'cause you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  現在我們已經來了\N{\b0\fs12}Now, look, we're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼不能呆一會兒呢\N{\b0\fs12}So why don't you just stay for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要跟別人說你的事  你只需要傾聽\N{\b0\fs12}You don't have to share or talk. You just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:13:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經說的很清楚了\N{\b0\fs12}I thought I made myself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我餓了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是一個人去吃飯吧\N{\b0\fs12}And now I think I'll eat alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧\N{\b0\fs12}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警署網站剛剛公佈了一起謀殺案\N{\b0\fs12}SCPD's network just lit up with a fresh homicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,死者身上有多處刺傷  像是爪子弄的\N{\b0\fs12}Multiple stab wounds. Like claw marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,受害人是一名建築師\N{\b0\fs12}The victim was an architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,特納洗劫了他的住所  拿走了他設計的圖紙\N{\b0\fs12}Turner ransacked his place; took blueprints of his designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他是馬爾科姆•梅林的房子的設計者之一\N{\b0\fs12}One of the aforementioned designs--Malcolm Merlyn's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我對建築學不太瞭解  但我知道這不是好事\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know much about architecture, but this can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,特納想從梅林的房子得到什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What would Turner want with Merlyn's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不清楚  馬爾科姆的所有產業\N{\b0\fs12}Not sure yet. All of Malcolm's holdings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,包括那棟房子  都處於破產受管狀態\N{\b0\fs12}including the house, are in receivership.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你在和誰講話\N{\b0\fs12}Who's that you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  讓我猜猜  這個你也不能告訴我\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, wait, let me guess, you can't tell me that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一個被我送進監獄的人越獄了\N{\b0\fs12}A guy that I put in prison got out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而我知道他會去哪\N{\b0\fs12}and I have an idea where he's headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有連帽衫嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you have one of your hoodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這還用問嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you seriously have to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼事  無論遇到什麼人\N{\b0\fs12}Whatever happens, whoever we run into,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,都不要理會\N{\b0\fs12}do not engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也不要碰\N{\b0\fs12}And don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這是他的孩子  對嗎\N{\b0\fs12}This is his kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,死掉的那個人的孩子\N{\b0\fs12}The guy that died?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\b0\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你很熟悉這裡\N{\b0\fs12}You know your way around this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前來過這兒嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,聲音是從地下傳出來的\N{\b0\fs12}It came from underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林有一個大的地下車庫\N{\b0\fs12}Merlyn has a large garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們走\N{\b0\fs12}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來像個原型機\N{\b0\fs12}Looks like a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼的原型機\N{\b0\fs12}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一個曾經殺死了503個人的機器的原型機\N{\b0\fs12}A machine that killed 503 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林自己的地震設備\N{\b0\fs12}Merlyn's own earthquake device.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  如探囊取物般簡單\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, a simple snatch and grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白為什麼阿米蒂奇先生要讓你跟著\N{\b0\fs12}Don't know why Mr. Armitage thought we needed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他們\N{\b0\fs12}For that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,離那臺設備遠點\N{\b0\fs12}Step away from the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不知道你們拿的是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}You don't know what it is you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是一臺能製造地震的大機器嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Big machine, makes earthquakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果它落到居心不良的人手中\N{\b0\fs12}Do you have any idea what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道會發生什麼事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}if the wrong people have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,知道  我收錢了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. I get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,關好門\N{\b0\fs12}Close it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那臺機器殺了我8個朋友\N{\b0\fs12}That thing killed eight of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\b0\fs12}That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來很生氣\N{\b0\fs12}Uh-oh. You got angry face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊•哈珀\N{\b0\fs12}Roy Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你帶他出去了\N{\b0\fs12}You took him out in the field--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾  他沒聽我的話\N{\b0\fs12}He wasn't listening to me, Diggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我試圖要抓住他  但他失去了控制\N{\b0\fs12}I'm trying to reach him, but he lost control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他差點殺了人\N{\b0\fs12}Then he nearly killed somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我當然不能讓他這麼幹  在這過程中\N{\b0\fs12}which I obviously couldn't let happen, and in the process--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,特納跑了\N{\b0\fs12}Turner got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他去那偷什麼  梅林的藝術收藏品嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What was he there to steal? Merlyn's art collection?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,比那要危險的多的東西\N{\b0\fs12}Something much more dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是一臺地震機的樣機\N{\b0\fs12}It's a prototype earthquake machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, holy god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼特納要毀掉這座城市\N{\b0\fs12}Why would Turner want to destroy the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有  他是一個雇傭兵\N{\b0\fs12}He doesn't. He's a mercenary
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他為出價最高的人服務\N{\b0\fs12}Selling his services to the highest bidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這塊表是其中一個\N{\b0\fs12}This watch belonged to one of the guys
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-和特納一起工作的人的  -有指紋\N{\b0\fs12}- Turner was working with. - Fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,特納是個獨行者  這意味著手錶的主人為特納的客戶工作\N{\b0\fs12}Turner's a loner, which mean that guy works for his client.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有了指紋就等於知道了名字  等於知道了他的同夥\N{\b0\fs12}Fingerprints equals name, equals known associates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上查\N{\b0\fs12}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在羅伊眼中看到的神情\N{\b0\fs12}It was the look in Roy's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,和斯萊德眼中的一模一樣\N{\b0\fs12}It was Slade all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  斯萊德發生了什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, what happened with Slade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\b0\fs12}Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有人殺了莎朵\N{\b0\fs12}Someone killed Shado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德愛過莎朵  而這是我的錯\N{\b0\fs12}Slade loved Shado, and it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要告訴他\N{\b0\fs12}I wanted to tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這從我口中說出比較好\N{\b0\fs12}because it would have been better coming from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我沒有\N{\b0\fs12}but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然後  他從其他途徑知道了\N{\b0\fs12}And he found out another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我直接告訴了他真相\N{\b0\fs12}If I had just told him the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能已經得到了他的諒解\N{\b0\fs12}I could have gotten through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而這就是為什麼  對你來說得到羅伊的諒解很重要\N{\b0\fs12}And that's why it's so important for you to get through to Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了5年的噩夢\N{\b0\fs12}I lived a five year nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我學到了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}But if I learn something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我現在能夠瞭解羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}that could help me reach Roy now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那所有的一切就都值得\N{\b0\fs12}it'll all be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在這兒\N{\b0\fs12}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那他能去哪兒  我們已經檢查過飛機了\N{\b0\fs12}Where else could he be? We already checked the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你記得之前見過這些嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you remember seeing these before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒四處看過\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't really look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這些看起來很眼熟\N{\b0\fs12}They look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這可能是煉獄島\N{\b0\fs12}This could be Lian Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是說這些演算\N{\b0\fs12}No, I mean the calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前見過\N{\b0\fs12}I've seen those before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是你第一次進山洞見到的\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe the first time you were in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不這麼認為\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-法爾斯的發射器  -什麼\N{\b0\fs12}- Fyer's launcher. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去年有部隊來過這個島\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, there were soldiers on the island last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他們有一個導彈發射器  他們演示時\N{\b0\fs12}And they had a missile launcher. I saw one of these
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到過其中一個   他們在進行發射計算\N{\b0\fs12}on the display. They're firing calculations...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要把那炸掉\N{\b0\fs12}He's going to blow it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把什麼炸掉\N{\b0\fs12}Blow what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,貨船\N{\b0\fs12}The freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,謝天謝地你在這  我需要你幫忙\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, thank god you're here, I need your help--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我有話要跟你說  這很重要\N{\b0\fs12}I have to talk to you. It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好  你看起來糟透了  沒什麼事吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ok. You look stressed out, is everything ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你得離開星城\N{\b0\fs12}You have to leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話  帶上你媽跟你哥  現在就離開\N{\b0\fs12}Grab your mother and your brother, if you can, and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,幾天就好\N{\b0\fs12}It's just for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,能給個解釋嗎\N{\b0\fs12}A reason would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你得相信我  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to trust me, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你  只是\N{\b0\fs12}I do. I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼能無緣無故就全家人離開呢\N{\b0\fs12}I can't up and leave with my family without a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但你必須走\N{\b0\fs12}No, you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你說的我完全聽不懂\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, you're not making any sense right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能告訴我到底發生了什麼事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Would you just tell me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼不聽我說呢\N{\b0\fs12}Why aren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你得聽我說\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你弄疼我了\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, you're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是...不是...\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't...I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有意的  對不起\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't mean to. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,離開創新聯合會後\N{\b0\fs12}Well. Your work environment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你的工作環境真是提高了不少\N{\b0\fs12}has definitely improved since CNRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這地方比我公寓還大呢\N{\b0\fs12}This place is bigger than my apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過外表的光鮮也是有局限的\N{\b0\fs12}Well, there is a limit to the glamour, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我整天都在處理文件\N{\b0\fs12}I spend my days in document production--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,回答問詢\N{\b0\fs12}and answering interrogatories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺都不像是跟法律相關\N{\b0\fs12}It doesn't feel like practicing law so much as
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,而是做文書了\N{\b0\fs12}pushing papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不瞭解的話  還真會以為\N{\b0\fs12}If I didn't know any better, I'd think
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要說服我不幹這份工作呢\N{\b0\fs12}that you were trying to talk me out of the job here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看來我還是有點自知\N{\b0\fs12}I guess I do know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的一位合夥人\N{\b0\fs12}One of the partners serves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是律師協會紀律委員會成員\N{\b0\fs12}on the Bar Association's Disciplinary Committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你的簡歷遞上去時\N{\b0\fs12}and...well, when I sent your resume,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他做了些背景調查\N{\b0\fs12}he did some checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那完全是個誤會\N{\b0\fs12}That was a complete misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  我是遇到了點麻煩\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, sure, yeah, I had some problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我現在沒事了\N{\b0\fs12}but I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,律師協會要進行紀律聽證會\N{\b0\fs12}The bar is going to open disciplinary proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,確定你是否還有能力繼續做律師\N{\b0\fs12}Conduct affecting your fitness to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這真是  真是太荒謬了\N{\b0\fs12}That's-- that's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但在這事塵埃落地前\N{\b0\fs12}But while this is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,事務所不能雇傭你\N{\b0\fs12}the firm can't hire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你告訴我  我得走了\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for letting me know. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你能度過這難關的  明白嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You can fight this, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我會幫助你\N{\b0\fs12}I'll help you, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要點時間來理清頭緒\N{\b0\fs12}I need some time to...process.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我再打給你\N{\b0\fs12}I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給你來點什麼喝的\N{\b0\fs12}Can I fix you a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你一樣就行\N{\b0\fs12}Whatever you're having.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那晚上見到你很開心  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}It was good to see you the other night, Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,的確不錯\N{\b0\fs12}It was lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我好久沒這麼開心地笑過了\N{\b0\fs12}It's been a while since I've had such a good laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是在說笑  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}It was no joke, Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,馬克說的是實話\N{\b0\fs12}Mark was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,星城的很多人都覺得\N{\b0\fs12}A significant number of people in Starling City
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫馬爾科姆•梅林做事\N{\b0\fs12}feel that your actions with Malcolm Merlyn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了保護你的家人\N{\b0\fs12}were justified to protect your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,事實上有43.6%的人這麼認為\N{\b0\fs12}43.6%, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你對我發起民意測驗\N{\b0\fs12}You polled people about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這是挑選候選人的\N{\b0\fs12}Prudent course of action when vetting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謹慎之舉  沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}a potential candidate, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,星城有六十萬人\N{\b0\fs12}600,000 people in Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你應該能找到一個\N{\b0\fs12}I'd think you could find someone not responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用地震機毀壞它的人來競選\N{\b0\fs12}for destroying it with an earthquake machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可你名聲在外\N{\b0\fs12}Not with your name recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要一個能力挽狂瀾的候選人  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}We need a game change candidate, Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而星城沒有人比你更德高望重了\N{\b0\fs12}And there's no one in Starling with a higher profile than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,查爾斯•曼森也挺有名的\N{\b0\fs12}Charles Manson is rather well-known,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}曼森家族曾在加州領導著臭名昭著犯罪團夥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-可沒人會投票給他  -沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}- and no one is going to vote for him. - True.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,同樣選民也喜歡自我救贖的故事\N{\b0\fs12}Equally true, voters like redemption stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,比爾•克林頓  艾略特•斯皮策[前紐約市長]\N{\b0\fs12}Bill Clinton, Elliot Spitzer,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}兩人均被性醜聞纏身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪莎•史都華\N{\b0\fs12}Martha Stewart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美國家政女神 曾因內幕交易被判自家中軟禁五個月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她可沒參加過競選\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I don't believe she ran for office.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果她參加了  肯定會贏的\N{\b0\fs12}But if she had, she would have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,會贏什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Would have won what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Ah, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}Mmm, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我在勸你媽媽參加市長競選\N{\b0\fs12}I'm just convincing your mother to run for mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼市長\N{\b0\fs12}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吧\N{\b0\fs12}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的  你還好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Sweetheart, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的別再問這問題了\N{\b0\fs12}You really need to stop asking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道這很難相信\N{\b0\fs12}It's hard to believe, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  並不是\N{\b0\fs12}No. No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這其實會是我有投票權後的第一回競選\N{\b0\fs12}Look, this is actually the first election I can vote in,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,作為一個新手選民\N{\b0\fs12}and...as a newly minted voter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:23:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這主意也不算太瘋狂\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think it sounds that crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,聽聽你寶貝女兒說的話\N{\b0\fs12}From out of the mouths of babes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你來晚了\N{\b0\fs12}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要我女朋友離開星城\N{\b0\fs12}I tried to get my girlfriend to leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.42,0:24:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但她不肯\N{\b0\fs12}But she won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不準把她牽扯進來\N{\b0\fs12}You cannot bring her into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.64,0:24:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可我要怎麼一邊隱瞞著她\N{\b0\fs12}But how am I supposed to lie to her
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.53,0:24:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊保護她呢\N{\b0\fs12}and protect her at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.55,0:24:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼做到的\N{\b0\fs12}How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.33,0:24:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼對你生活中的人隱瞞事實真相\N{\b0\fs12}How do you keep secrets from people in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.62,0:24:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只要記住這是唯一保證他們安全的辦法\N{\b0\fs12}By remembering it's the only way to keep them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.94,0:24:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不  要讓他們安全才能保證安全\N{\b0\fs12}No, keeping them safe is what keeps them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.47,0:24:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,該告訴他們真相\N{\b0\fs12}Telling people the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可你什麼都不願跟我說\N{\b0\fs12}But you, you won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.68,0:24:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不說米拉庫魯  還有那個傢伙\N{\b0\fs12}Not about the Mirakuru, and this other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.82,0:24:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,卻讓我在這傻子一樣拍水跟打木頭人\N{\b0\fs12}And you got me slapping water and hitting dummies instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.96,0:24:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你現在太激動了  需要冷靜下來\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, you're spiraling and you need to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.50,0:24:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我需要去救西婭\N{\b0\fs12}No. I need to save Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.16,0:24:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為你那傢伙才跑出去了\N{\b0\fs12}That thing is out in the open because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.52,0:24:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫的忙夠多了\N{\b0\fs12}I think you've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.71,0:24:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我\N{\b0\fs12}Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.33,0:25:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-羅伊  -我說了放開我\N{\b0\fs12}- Roy... - I said let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.21,0:25:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,控制一下你自己\N{\b0\fs12}Get control.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.60,0:25:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不為我  不為你自己\N{\b0\fs12}If not for me or yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.99,0:25:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也為了西婭\N{\b0\fs12}then do it for Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.72,0:25:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你他媽對西婭有什麼瞭解\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell do you know about Thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,別跟我說她\N{\b0\fs12}Don't you talk about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.93,0:25:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你鬧夠了沒\N{\b0\fs12}Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.13,0:25:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我沒夠\N{\b0\fs12}No. I'm not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.51,0:25:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去阻止那傢伙\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to stop this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.27,0:25:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是想阻止我  就試試\N{\b0\fs12}And if you want to stop me, try.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再給我一箭  來啊\N{\b0\fs12}Try putting another arrow in me. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.82,0:25:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在恢復得很快  但如果你擋我的路\N{\b0\fs12}'Cause I heal fast now. But you get in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.14,0:25:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我就讓你好好看看你所擔心的\N{\b0\fs12}then I'll give you a good look at that anger you're so worried
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去控制發怒會怎樣\N{\b0\fs12}about me losing control of.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.68,0:25:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我說我們應該在這下麵裝一臺X光機的時候\N{\b0\fs12}You both scoffed when I said we should invest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.54,0:25:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆都嘲笑我\N{\b0\fs12}in an x-ray machine for down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.82,0:26:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要怎麼處理羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}What do you want to do about Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,指紋查的怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}Where are we with the fingerprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.41,0:26:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我略過了國內的機構\N{\b0\fs12}I struck out on domestic agencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.02,0:26:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,現在在查國際刑警  中國公安\N{\b0\fs12}but I'm checking Interpol, PRC Public Security
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.69,0:26:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,以及俄羅斯內務部的數據庫\N{\b0\fs12}and MVD databases now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.75,0:26:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  我知道你要幫羅伊  也知道為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, I know you've taken Roy on, and why,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.99,0:26:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是羅伊  斯萊德  很多我共事過的人...\N{\b0\fs12}but Roy, Slade, a lot of guys I've served with...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.85,0:26:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人已經喪失心智了  夥計\N{\b0\fs12}Some people are just broken, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,無藥可救了\N{\b0\fs12}And nobody can put them back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.49,0:26:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒絕相信這些\N{\b0\fs12}I refuse to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.91,0:26:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓發生在斯萊德身上的事\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not letting what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.32,0:26:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再發生到羅伊身上\N{\b0\fs12}to Slade happen to Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.38,0:26:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.47,0:26:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.91,0:26:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在俱樂部附近嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you near the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.14,0:26:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,離得很近  怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm pretty close. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.21,0:26:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起來不太好\N{\b0\fs12}She doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.46,0:26:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾在樓上\N{\b0\fs12}Hey. Laurel's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.76,0:27:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.62,0:27:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能給我杯帶橄欖的飲料嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can I get something with olives?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.38,0:27:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼飲料無所謂  只要有很多橄欖就行\N{\b0\fs12}I don't care what it is, as long as there are a lot of olives.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.36,0:27:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}How about coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.19,0:27:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡和橄欖\N{\b0\fs12}Coffee and olives?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.45,0:27:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這組合不好\N{\b0\fs12}Bad combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.08,0:27:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.29,0:27:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在這裡發生的  是不是  大俱樂部\N{\b0\fs12}This is where it's happening, right? The big club?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.76,0:27:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,給  你的馬提尼  三顆橄欖\N{\b0\fs12}Here you go, martini, triple olives.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.45,0:27:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.12,0:27:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  回家吧\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭•奎恩告訴我\N{\b0\fs12}Thea Queen, telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.48,0:27:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了就是夠了\N{\b0\fs12}enough is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.89,0:27:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,現在有錢了\N{\b0\fs12}Now that is rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.66,0:27:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.01,0:27:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,取消我進你酒吧的資格\N{\b0\fs12}Bar me from your bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.62,0:27:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是今天的主題  是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}That's today's theme, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.58,0:27:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,取消資格\N{\b0\fs12}Disbarment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.63,0:27:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  你被取消律師資格了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, are you being disbarred?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.09,0:27:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  看起來我的律師生涯結束了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, looks like my law career's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.88,0:27:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道嗎\N{\b0\fs12}But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.98,0:27:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,或許西婭可以雇我當服務員\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe Thea here can hire me as a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.26,0:28:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或者  奧利  我可以給你當秘書\N{\b0\fs12}Or, Ollie, I could come be your secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.51,0:28:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但這意味著你要解雇她\N{\b0\fs12}But that would mean you would have to fire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.31,0:28:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  勞蕾爾  你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Hi, Laurel. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.23,0:28:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你要借我的車嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Did you need to borrow my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.90,0:28:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的豪車壞了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Did your limo break down?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.46,0:28:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,請幫她叫輛計程車\N{\b0\fs12}Get her a cab, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.25,0:28:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,指紋在國際刑警數據庫有\N{\b0\fs12}Fingerprint was in Interpol's database.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.02,0:28:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是米洛•阿米蒂奇的手下\N{\b0\fs12}The guy worked for Milo Armitage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.65,0:28:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他是個黑市軍火商\N{\b0\fs12}He's a black market arms merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.37,0:28:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他想賣掉那儀器\N{\b0\fs12}He's trying to sell the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.18,0:28:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找找阿米蒂奇\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to search for any indication
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.66,0:28:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在星城的任何蛛絲馬跡\N{\b0\fs12}that Armitage is in Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.92,0:28:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已經找了  他的船在星城碼頭\N{\b0\fs12}I already did. His ship filed a loading manifest
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.49,0:28:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,提交了一張裝貨單\N{\b0\fs12}at the Starling City docks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.81,0:28:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把船號給你\N{\b0\fs12}I'll get you the slip number.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.18,0:28:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我是奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Hi, it's Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.07,0:28:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛剛碰到勞蕾爾  她出事了\N{\b0\fs12}I just ran into Laurel, and something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要你\N{\b0\fs12}She needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.35,0:29:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.96,0:29:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.95,0:29:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.52,0:29:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,回來\N{\b0\fs12}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.47,0:29:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們知道你的目標是那艘船\N{\b0\fs12}We know you're targeting the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.00,0:29:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把那混蛋\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to send that son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.84,0:29:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,送到海底\N{\b0\fs12}to the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.97,0:29:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你要毀掉我們離開這個島的唯一出路\N{\b0\fs12}You're going to destroy our only way off of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.41,0:29:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只要艾沃死了  那就行\N{\b0\fs12}As long as Ivo is dead, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.70,0:29:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能讓你這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}I can't let you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.50,0:29:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,後退  不然就幫我\N{\b0\fs12}Get back, or so help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.61,0:29:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我會放到你的\N{\b0\fs12}I will put you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  你在這兒幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Mom? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.64,0:29:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我來徵求一下你的意見\N{\b0\fs12}I came by to get your advice on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.85,0:29:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,到我辦公室來\N{\b0\fs12}Step into my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.49,0:29:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是選舉的事  是不是\N{\b0\fs12}This is about the campaign, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.59,0:29:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想到參與這事非常的棒\N{\b0\fs12}It's really awesome you're thinking of doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的某些話我一直揮之不去\N{\b0\fs12}You said something that stayed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.45,0:29:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可能外面有投票人\N{\b0\fs12}The idea that there could be voters out there
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.87,0:29:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不會立刻就讓我卸任\N{\b0\fs12}that wouldn't dismiss me out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.79,0:29:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的確經營著一家數十億美元的公司\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you did run a multi-billion dollar company.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.79,0:30:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  還做了一件毀了城市的事\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, and an undertaking that destroyed the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.72,0:30:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,人們會慢慢忘記的\N{\b0\fs12}People will get over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.52,0:30:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼能這麼確定\N{\b0\fs12}What makes you so certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.06,0:30:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我就是\N{\b0\fs12}Because I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.68,0:30:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我能提個建議嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can I make a suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.89,0:30:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再因為覺得自己毀了城市而自責\N{\b0\fs12}Instead of punishing yourself because you think you destroyed the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.59,0:30:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,開始著手拯救這城市怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}how about you start by saving it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.49,0:30:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一千萬美元\N{\b0\fs12}$10 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.66,0:30:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想這是說好的價格\N{\b0\fs12}I believe was the negotiated amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.91,0:30:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜  你現在進入新的納稅階層了\N{\b0\fs12}Congratulations, you're now in a new tax bracket.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.31,0:30:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只是出於好奇\N{\b0\fs12}Just out of curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.63,0:30:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你付給我一千萬美元  那你能得到...\N{\b0\fs12}you pay me ten million, and you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.36,0:30:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這價錢的三倍\N{\b0\fs12}Three times that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.22,0:30:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經有買家了\N{\b0\fs12}You already have a buyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.58,0:30:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我建議你遠離馬庫維亞幾個月\N{\b0\fs12}I recommend that you stay clear of Markovia for a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.36,0:30:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我們的生意到此結束了\N{\b0\fs12}I believe our business is now concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.54,0:30:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有\N{\b0\fs12}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.25,0:31:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來你的搭檔拋棄你了\N{\b0\fs12}Looks like your partner abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.73,0:31:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是我的搭檔\N{\b0\fs12}He's not my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.05,0:31:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我雇來做事的\N{\b0\fs12}He's someone I hired to do a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.48,0:31:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看來這筆錢花的值\N{\b0\fs12}And it turns out it was money well spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.96,0:31:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下太愚蠢了\N{\b0\fs12}Just too dumb to stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.57,0:31:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.98,0:31:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你會殺死這裡的所有人\N{\b0\fs12}You'll kill everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.97,0:31:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不把這儀器送到馬庫維亞的買家手裡\N{\b0\fs12}If I don't deliver this device to my buyer in Markovia,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.66,0:31:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一樣死定了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm dead anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.14,0:31:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.68,0:32:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  我需要你的幫助\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.48,0:32:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  馬上住手\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, stop right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.91,0:32:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-羅伊  -混蛋\N{\b0\fs12}- Roy. - Son of bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.07,0:32:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  羅伊  住手\N{\b0\fs12}Roy! Roy, I need you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.78,0:32:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,地震儀器就在裡面\N{\b0\fs12}The earthquake device is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.75,0:32:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這鋼是軍事級別的  能抵擋炸彈\N{\b0\fs12}The steel is military grade; it's built to withstand a bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.39,0:32:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是抵擋不了你\N{\b0\fs12}but not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.48,0:32:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想想西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Think about Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.86,0:32:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒有你的幫助  她可能會死\N{\b0\fs12}Because she could die without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.57,0:32:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你愛她...\N{\b0\fs12}I know you love her...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.81,0:32:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我看見了\N{\b0\fs12}Because I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.04,0:32:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我的妹妹\N{\b0\fs12}Save my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.23,0:32:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,控制住\N{\b0\fs12}Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.89,0:32:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,集中注意力想西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Focus on Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.17,0:32:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在需要你\N{\b0\fs12}She needs you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.14,0:32:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,否則她就會死\N{\b0\fs12}or she is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.88,0:32:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都會死\N{\b0\fs12}Everyone is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.85,0:33:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你是...\N{\b0\fs12}You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.97,0:33:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,對  沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.89,0:33:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去年  你救了我的命\N{\b0\fs12}Last year, you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.47,0:33:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說從綁架我的人手裡\N{\b0\fs12}And I don't mean from the guy who kidnapped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.03,0:33:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說  你...\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.67,0:33:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你拯救了我\N{\b0\fs12}you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.73,0:33:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你給了我目標\N{\b0\fs12}You gave me purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.69,0:33:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才剛剛開始\N{\b0\fs12}We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.01,0:33:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...秘密組織有了個新成員\N{\b0\fs12}So...the secret society gets a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.98,0:33:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他現在在哪\N{\b0\fs12}Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.08,0:33:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在家\N{\b0\fs12}Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.70,0:33:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他還在...\N{\b0\fs12}He's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.95,0:33:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,消化這事\N{\b0\fs12}processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.25,0:34:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,當我知道你的真實身份時\N{\b0\fs12}When I found out who you really were,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.70,0:34:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃了一品脫的薄荷片才接受這個事實\N{\b0\fs12}I processed my way through a pint of mint chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.63,0:34:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我壓力大就吃東西\N{\b0\fs12}I stress eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.33,0:34:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,說到壓力...\N{\b0\fs12}Speaking of stress...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.15,0:34:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是想開周一例會  今天週三\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not trying to Monday morning quarterback here--it's Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.00,0:34:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切不都是因為你擔心\N{\b0\fs12}Didn't this all start because you were worried
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.74,0:34:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊的力量會被壞人利用嗎\N{\b0\fs12}that Roy's marble collection was on the short side?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.55,0:34:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她說得有理  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}She has a point, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.23,0:34:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊是匹野馬  現在他知道你的秘密了\N{\b0\fs12}Roy's a loose cannon. Now he knows your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.30,0:34:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對\N{\b0\fs12}You're right,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.17,0:34:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但我沒考慮後果\N{\b0\fs12}and I wasn't thinking about the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.50,0:34:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道我需要他的力量\N{\b0\fs12}I only knew that I needed his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.33,0:34:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的力量\N{\b0\fs12}His power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.02,0:34:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在島上\N{\b0\fs12}On the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.88,0:34:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉告訴我愛是最強大的情感\N{\b0\fs12}Sara told me that love is the most powerful emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.34,0:34:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,綠箭俠不能讓羅伊想到西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Well, the Arrow couldn't get Roy to think about Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.04,0:34:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可以\N{\b0\fs12}But I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.87,0:35:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了後退\N{\b0\fs12}I said get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想想莎朵\N{\b0\fs12}Think about Shado.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.22,0:35:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我在...\N{\b0\fs12}I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.55,0:35:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想著她\N{\b0\fs12}thinking about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.53,0:35:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我得告訴你一件關於莎朵的事\N{\b0\fs12}There's something I have to tell you about Shado.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.05,0:35:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是一件你需要知道的事\N{\b0\fs12}It's something you deserve to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.27,0:35:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她愛你  斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}She loved you, Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也許不是以你想要的方式\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe not the way that you wanted her to,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.94,0:35:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但她愛你\N{\b0\fs12}but she loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.17,0:35:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她想讓你回家\N{\b0\fs12}And she wanted you to make it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.47,0:35:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她想讓你再見到喬\N{\b0\fs12}She wanted you to see Joe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.60,0:35:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她想讓你擁抱你的兒子\N{\b0\fs12}She wanted you to hug your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.47,0:35:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很憤怒\N{\b0\fs12}I know you're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.78,0:35:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道你想復仇\N{\b0\fs12}And I know you want revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.71,0:35:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你毀了艾沃的貨船\N{\b0\fs12}If you destroy Ivo's freighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.79,0:35:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莎朵就白白犧牲了\N{\b0\fs12}Shado will have died for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.61,0:36:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What is happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.92,0:36:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.43,0:36:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你一個人\N{\b0\fs12}I am not going to let you go through it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.95,0:36:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,承受這些的\N{\b0\fs12}on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.79,0:36:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了莎朵的那個人\N{\b0\fs12}The man who killed Shado
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.62,0:36:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒被抓到\N{\b0\fs12}is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.03,0:36:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而不管那艘貨船沉沒沒有\N{\b0\fs12}And whether that freighter's on the bottom of the ocean or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.80,0:36:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都還被困在這個島上\N{\b0\fs12}we're still stuck on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.48,0:36:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不會很久的\N{\b0\fs12}Not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.41,0:36:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們要乘那艘貨船回家\N{\b0\fs12}Because we're going to take the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.02,0:36:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興收到你的郵件\N{\b0\fs12}I was glad to receive your email.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.06,0:36:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是跟我想的一樣\N{\b0\fs12}Does it portend what I'm hoping?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.02,0:36:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去參加競選\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.32,0:36:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼讓你改變主意的\N{\b0\fs12}What changed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.92,0:37:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.26,0:37:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她提醒我我還欠這座城市的\N{\b0\fs12}She reminded me that I still owe this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.26,0:37:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想被世人銘記  而不是作為\N{\b0\fs12}And I want to be remembered as something more
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.64,0:37:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾科姆•梅林的傀儡\N{\b0\fs12}than Malcolm Merlyn's pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.88,0:37:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該被人記住\N{\b0\fs12}As you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.00,0:37:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道我的猶豫還有別的原因\N{\b0\fs12}But you know there was another reason for my reticence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.74,0:37:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕別人知道\N{\b0\fs12}You're afraid the people will learn
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.00,0:37:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伯特不是她的親生父親\N{\b0\fs12}that Robert wasn't her biological father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.27,0:37:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我設法在不說出\N{\b0\fs12}I managed to get through a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.44,0:37:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真相的情況下通過了審判\N{\b0\fs12}criminal trial without the truth coming out,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.31,0:37:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但政治選舉能更容易地挖出\N{\b0\fs12}but political campaigns tend to be a bit more adept
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.20,0:37:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人罪惡的秘密\N{\b0\fs12}at extracting skeletons from closets.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.15,0:37:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但沒有別人知道\N{\b0\fs12}But no one else knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.72,0:37:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有人知道\N{\b0\fs12}Someone does.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.90,0:37:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的婦產科醫生  吉爾醫生\N{\b0\fs12}My OB, Dr. Gill.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.65,0:37:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭出生時情況很複雜\N{\b0\fs12}There were complications when Thea was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.65,0:37:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不告訴他羅伯特不是她父親\N{\b0\fs12}And I had to tell him that Robert wasn't her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.89,0:37:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們要發展下去\N{\b0\fs12}If we're going to move forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.61,0:37:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得確定\N{\b0\fs12}we need to make certain
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.20,0:37:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會成為我們的問題\N{\b0\fs12}that he won't be a problem for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.23,0:38:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,特納先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.99,0:38:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道這裡還允許配偶探視\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't know this place allowed conjugal visits.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.90,0:38:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阿曼達•沃勒\N{\b0\fs12}My name is Amanda Waller.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.72,0:38:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的好像你很有名\N{\b0\fs12}You say that like it's supposed to mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.72,0:38:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,正好相反\N{\b0\fs12}To the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.36,0:38:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身份是高度機密\N{\b0\fs12}My identity is highly classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.01,0:38:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼向我做自我介紹\N{\b0\fs12}Then why are you introducing yourself to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.15,0:38:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個工作機會給你\N{\b0\fs12}I have an offer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.99,0:38:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一個讓你減刑的方法\N{\b0\fs12}A way to work off your sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.99,0:38:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,事實證明  我需要一個像你一樣...\N{\b0\fs12}As it turns out, I have need of someone with your...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.02,0:38:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,天賦異稟的人\N{\b0\fs12}singular qualifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.62,0:38:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.75,0:38:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為了一支我正在組建的部隊\N{\b0\fs12}For a unit I'm putting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.63,0:38:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的部隊\N{\b0\fs12}What type of unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.15,0:38:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,實際上...\N{\b0\fs12}Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.38,0:38:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,更像是一支小隊\N{\b0\fs12}It's more of a squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.50,0:38:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了你的秘密你會殺了我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is this the part where you kill me 'cause I know your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.35,0:39:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我會殺了我妹妹的男朋友嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you actually think that I'd kill my sister's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.86,0:39:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可你曾經往我腿上射了一箭\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you did shoot me in the leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我已經原諒你了\N{\b0\fs12}Forgiven, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.12,0:39:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.69,0:39:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠不能讓她知道\N{\b0\fs12}She can never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.75,0:39:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得如果我告訴她的話\N{\b0\fs12}I get the feeling that if I did tell her,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.10,0:39:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的會殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}that would be when you kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.38,0:39:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,相信你的直覺\N{\b0\fs12}Trust that instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.12,0:39:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ok. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.81,0:39:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少人知道\N{\b0\fs12}How many people know what--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.19,0:39:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰\N{\b0\fs12}who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.51,0:39:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很多\N{\b0\fs12}Too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.16,0:39:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有這兩個比較重要\N{\b0\fs12}But these are the only two that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.67,0:39:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,約翰•狄格爾和費利西蒂•斯莫克\N{\b0\fs12}John Diggle and Felicity Smoak.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.53,0:39:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這個團隊有名字嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Does this group have a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.85,0:39:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,比如綠箭隊之類的\N{\b0\fs12}Like Team Arrow, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.24,0:39:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不那麼稱呼自己\N{\b0\fs12}We don't call ourselves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.78,0:39:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我會  偶爾會\N{\b0\fs12}I do. Occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.69,0:39:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-停  -無所謂\N{\b0\fs12}- Stop.  - Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.45,0:39:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎加入\N{\b0\fs12}Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.48,0:40:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉...\N{\b0\fs12}Sara...